/*
    NTX Setup Manager — Stylesheet Entry Point
    ------------------------------------------
    Styles are now loaded from numbered modules in:
        styles/modules/

    Module load order (lexicographic):
        10-base.qss              — typography, navigation rail, label tokens
        20-inputs-scrollbars.qss — text inputs and scrollbars
        40-buttons.qss           — button hierarchy (primary, secondary, nav)
        50-data-views.qss        — tables, tabs, group boxes, dialogs
        60-catalog.qss           — work list cards (matching Tool Library style)
        80-layout-overrides.qss  — splitter handles and small tweaks

    To change a style, edit the relevant module file.
    This file is kept as a fallback only; modules take precedence when present.
*/
